sec.p: There were no differences between species in laying date (F 1,179 = 1.60; P = 0.27), hatching date (F 1,179 = 0.74; P = 0.43) or clutch size (F 1,179 = 4.58; P = 0.08). There were also no differences between years in laying date (F 1,179 = 1.62; P = 0.25), hatching date (F 1,179 = 1.17; P = 0.33) or clutch size (F 1,179 = 1.05; P = 0.39).
